Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Kearns.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Kearns (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 77.]

(No. 93-456 Submitted April 20, 1993 Decided August 11, 1993.) *78J. Warren Bettis, Disciplinary Counsel, and Sally Ann Steuk, Assistant Disciplinary Counsel, for relator. George H. Kearns, pro se. Per Curiam.

Upon review of the record, we agree with the findings and recommendation of the board. George H. Kearns is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
